other_title: La Rana Valiente - Hiroshi y Raponchi (Spanish)
plot: When Hiroshi was fighting against his rival Gorillaimo, he stumble over a stone and fell on to a frog. To be surprised, the frog was still alive and it named itself Pyonkichi.

ending_theme: "Dokonjo de Yansu" (ど根性でヤンス) by Susumu Ishikawa
"Dokonjo Gaeru Ondo" (ど根性ガエル音頭) by Susumu Ishikawa, Arakawa Shounen Shoujo Gasshou-tai, Sachiko Chijimatsu
